- Make "diet" variant of backup. This variant will erase all unnecessary daily and weekly backups during cleaning procedure.
- Make SVN module
- Make Oracle module
- Add functionality in MySQL module to backup selected databasees instead of whole DB.
- Add new functionality to files module. This functionality will examine target directory, create tree structure and make sorted backup to these directories.
  For example: With this, you'll be able to backup Maildirs easily.
- New config variable. This variable will define backup skipping. It will be something like cron syntax.
- Update config sample to include all modules and configuration samples. Or remove sample and write documentation.
- Pymssql is unfortunately obsolete, implement future version of mssql module in pyodbc.